**Source:** ChatGPT (GPT 5.4) via SECURITY.md defense verification prompt
**Date:** 2026-03-17
**Findings:** 1 Medium (novel — corrects prior characterization from 4 other audits)

## Post-Review Responses

| # | Finding | Action | Rationale |
|---:|---|---|---|
| M-1 | Partial-claim truncation overpays vesting schedule | **Fixed** | Valid novel finding. All prior audits (Pashov, Grimoire, internal) characterized this truncation as "dust loss" — GPT 5.4 correctly proved the direction is overpayment. `claimed` is now rounded down to whole seconds before transfer. |

